Parallelized implementation of Maximum Entropy and Naive Bayesian classifier. 

In order to run the tests:

1. Make sure that you have Java 1.6, Scala 2.9 and sbt 0.11

2. Install Menthor
	$ git clone git@github.com:stanvp/menthor.git
	$ cd menthor
	$ git checkout distributed
	$ sbt
	> project libmenthor
	> set publishArtifact in packageDoc := false // avoid scaladoc generation error
	> publish-local
	 
3. Get the project 
	$ git clone https://github.com/stanvp/parallelnlp
	$ cd parallelnlp	
	$ sbt assembly
	$ wget -c http://nltk.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/nltk_data/packages/corpora/movie_reviews.zip
	$ unzip movie_reviews.zip	
	$ java -Xmx2048m -XX:MaxPermSize=256m -cp target/parallelnlp-assembly-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar menthor.apps.NaiveBayesClassifierMovieReview parallel movie_reviews
	$ java -Xmx2048m -XX:MaxPermSize=256m -cp target/parallelnlp-assembly-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar menthor.apps.MaxentClassifierMovieReview parallel movie_reviews
	
You can also use sequential version by passing sequential instead of parallel in the parameters above.  